<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="579" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,845,1673]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,326,1610,1636]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">Etymology</emphasis>
. The specific epithet refers to the male aedeagus vesica shape, which is the longest in the speciesgroup.
</paragraph>
